information_for_contributors: This file has been converted from https://github.com/atom/language-objective-c/blob/master/grammars/objective-c.cson
If you want to provide a fix or improvement, please create a pull request against the original repository.
Once accepted there, we are happy to receive an update request.
name: Objective-C

patterns.match:
(?x)%
						(\d+\$)?                             # field (argument #)
						[#0\- +']*                          # flags
						((-?\d+)|\*(-?\d+\$)?)?              # minimum field width
						(\.((-?\d+)|\*(-?\d+\$)?)?)?         # precision
						[@]                                  # conversion type
patterns.name: constant.other.placeholder.objc
